  "attack": {
    "name": "Allegoria",
    "description": "<span style=\"color: #FFD780FF;\">Normal Attack</span>\\nProclaims a decree in the primordial tongue and performs up to 3 attacks that deal <span style=\"color: #FF9999FF;\">Pyro DMG</span>.\\n\\n<span style=\"color: #FFD780FF;\">Charged Attack</span>\\nConsumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal <span style=\"color: #FF9999FF;\">AoE Pyro DMG</span> to opponents in front of her after a short casting time.\\n\\n<span style=\"color: #FFD780FF;\">Plunging Attack</span>\\nNicole plunges towards the ground from mid-air, damaging all opponents in her path. Also deals <span style=\"color: #FF9999FF;\">AoE Pyro DMG</span> upon impact with the ground.",
